import { Message_ } from "../message/messageSlice" import "./UserMessageStyle.css" export default function UserMessage(props:any){ let messages:Message_ = props.messages let display = props.display let MessageDisplay = "" let messageLength = messages.FoodName.length let marginLeft = messageLength * 13 return(
{messages.FoodName}
{messages.count}
{messages.cost}
{messages.date}
) }
